last_episode_to_air.name: Pups Save the Super Cows
last_episode_to_air.overview: Winnie's cow competitor Moona Lisa and Bettina run away during the Super Farm Fair.

name: PAW Patrol
overview: PAW Patrol is a CG action-adventure for old children and preschool series starring a pack of six heroic puppies led by a tech-savvy 10-year-old boy named Ryder.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: The PAW Patrol pups take their adventures to the sky with an all-new rescue vehicle, the Air Patroller, that can transport Ryder and the gang anywhere in the world. The third season also introduces new friends including Tracker, a jeep-driving pup with super hearing who lives in the jungle with Carlos.

episodes.name: Pups and the Kitty-tastrophe
episodes.overview: A kitten named Precious is floating out to sea, and the PAW Patrol must rescue her, but that's not all. The PAW Patrol must also act fast to find her owner before the mischievous kitten gets into big trouble.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Train
episodes.overview: The train that Katie and Cali are on is stuck on a bridge because of a rock slide. The PAW Patrol must act fast since the broken bridge beam can't hold the train for long!

episodes.name: Pup Pup Boogie
episodes.overview: A train car falls off the tracks and also breaks some rails. A train is coming later with important packages in it, with the all new Pup Pup Boogie 2.0 dance game. The PAW Patrol tries to fix the tracks, but how will they fix the tracks when Rubble sprains his paw and can't work? Can Chase save the day?

episodes.name: Pups in a Fog
episodes.overview: While the pups are having a sleepover, the Lighthouse light runs out of power. Cap'n Turbot, the one who monitors the Lighthouse light, is out at sea.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Sea Turtles
episodes.overview: Baby sea turtles were hatching at the other side of the road near the beach. They can't get to the beach without crossing the street, there are cars, skateboarders, scooters and all the hungry naughty seagulls around, not to mention Alex's rambunctious antics.

episodes.name: Pups and the Very Big Baby
episodes.overview: A baby whale has beached herself. The PAW Patrol has to rescue her and make sure her mother doesn't get too close. Can they save her and reunite her with her mother?

episodes.name: Pups Save the Circus
episodes.overview: Ellie, the baby elephant from the Circus train, has escaped and is loose in Adventure Bay!

episodes.name: Pup a Doodle Do
episodes.overview: Mayor Goodway's purse chicken, Chickaleta, is on the loose and the PAW Patrol must find her before it's too late for Mayor Goodway and Chickaleta to host Hello, Adventure Bay.

episodes.name: Pup Pup Goose
episodes.overview: When a flock of migrating geese stops in Adventure Bay, Marshall bonds with Fuzzy, the gosling of the flock.

episodes.name: Pup Pup and Away
episodes.overview: Mayor Goodway has entered the Mayor's Hot Air Balloon Race, and she wants to beat the arrogant Mayor Humdinger of Foggy Bottom, but her balloon has a hole in it.

episodes.name: Pups Pit Crew
episodes.overview: The pups help a young boy named Alex fix his broken tricycle and teach him a valuable lesson of taking new things slow.

episodes.name: Pups Fight Fire
episodes.overview: The pups helps Marshall prepare for a firefighting obstacle course to win the fastest fire pup trophy.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Bunnies
episodes.overview: A bunch of adorable bunnies have come to Farmer Yumi's carrot patch. The PAW Patrol must catch them all and relocate them to a perfect new home.

episodes.name: Pup-Tacular
episodes.overview: While the rest of the PAW Patrol are out to rescue Mayor Goodway and Chickaleta and checking the trucks, Rocky must face his hydrophobia so that Katie can enter him in the Pup-Tacular Show.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Bay
episodes.overview: There's an oil spill in the bay, and a Baby Whale swam into the oil. The PAW Patrol must clean up the Baby Whale and the oil spill before more animals living in Adventure Bay are harmed by it.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Goodway
episodes.overview: It's Great-Great-Great-Great-Grandpa Grover Day, and Mayor Goodway has been planning anxiously for today's celebration.

episodes.name: Pups Get a Rubble
episodes.overview: This episode is a flashback story of how Rubble joined the PAW Patrol. Rubble must help Jake when he gets trapped in an Avalanche.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Walrus
episodes.overview: The playful walrus, Wally, was performing tricks for Cap'n Turbot, but he eventually gets himself tangled in a fishing net during one of his tricks.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Treats
episodes.overview: On a snow and icy day, Mr. Porter's van ends up sliding on ice. If the ice cracks, it will fall into the bottom of the bay, and inside of the truck has all the pups' treats and food in it!

episodes.name: Pups Get a Lift
episodes.overview: Katie and Cali are stuck on Jake's Mountain. Rubble wants Ryder to pick him but he picks Marshall and Rocky.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Hoedown
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol are having a great time at the Adventure Bay Hoedown, but trouble starts to brew when Farmer Al's cows get spooked out and are on the loose in Adventure Bay.

episodes.name: Pups Save Alex
episodes.overview: While Cali is playing with her favorite toy on Farmer Yumi's farm, she gets stuck on the top of the silo, which is not safe.

episodes.name: Pups and the Ghost Pirate
episodes.overview: A Halloween party turns into a spooky time when there's a ghostly figure roaming around on a ship. Can the PAW Patrol solve the paranormal mystery and save the Halloween party?

episodes.name: Pups Save a School Day
episodes.overview: It's Alex's first day of school, but he has lost his backpack! So the PAW Patrol agrees to help him find it.

episodes.name: Pups Turn On the Lights
episodes.overview: It's Chase's birthday and the other pups and Katie are setting up Chase's surprise birthday party at Katie's Clinic.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Pool Day
episodes.overview: It's a hot day and the pups head for the water park, but the pool is empty! The water tower that pumps water into the pool is tilted and has a bent pipe.

episodes.name: Circus Pup-formers
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol, for the first time, must all work together to help Eunice and Ellie save the circus when most of the performers are late.

episodes.name: Pups Make a Splash
episodes.overview: Cap'n Turbot got The Flounder stuck on some rocks. If the PAW Patrol doesn't save him, The Flounder will sink to the bottom of the bay!

episodes.name: Pups Fall Festival
episodes.overview: Ryder and the PAW Patrol have to save Farmer Yumi's fruit before an early snowfall comes. Everyone has a job to do to help, except for Chase.

episodes.name: Pups Save Christmas
episodes.overview: Santa's sleigh crashes and breaks in a snow storm on Christmas Eve, and all the presents are strewn across Adventure Bay. It's up to the PAW Patrol to fix the sled, collect the reindeer, find the gifts, find the magic star, and most importantly, save Christmas for Adventure Bay.

episodes.name: Pups On Ice
episodes.overview: Ryder and the PAW Patrol need to rescue Alex on Jakes mountain.

episodes.name: Pups and the Snow Monster
episodes.overview: The pups find strange footprints in the snow on the mountain outside Adventure Bay. Everyone thinks it's a "snow monster" and it's scaring the skiers away.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Super Pup
episodes.overview: Rubble is pretending to be a super pup and tries to handle a rescue all by himself, but soon, Ryder and the Paw Patrol have to save Rubble.

episodes.name: Pups Save Ryder's Robot
episodes.overview: When Ryder's Robot Pup breaks and starts going wild around Adventure Bay, it takes the whole Paw Patrol to help Ryder find it.

episodes.name: Pups Go All Monkey
episodes.overview: An escaped baby monkey named Mandy leads the PAW Patrol on a chase through Adventure Bay, when she steals Mr. Porter van full of bananas.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Hoot
episodes.overview: Chase befriends a baby owl and with the PAW Patrol helps rescue its mother who is trapped in the knothole of a fallen tree.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Bat
episodes.overview: A baby Bat decides to take a nap hanging from the Town Hall's bell and Mayor Goodway can't ring it. Ryder and the Pups attempt to rescue the bat quietly so it doesn't wake up, but it does and causes trouble around town. It's up to Ryder and the Pups to get the Bat and return her to her Bat cave.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Toof
episodes.overview: Alex is afraid to go to the dentist, so Chase and the PAW Patrol work together to show Alex that fears can be overcome.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Easter Egg Hunt
episodes.overview: It’s Adventure Bay’s annual Easter Egg Hunt and the pups are helping Mayor Goodway with the egg decorating. The hunt for a very special egg leads Ryder and the PAW Patrol on an exciting adventure.

episodes.name: Pups and the Lighthouse Boogie
episodes.overview: Cap'n Turbot has accidentally locked himself inside the lighthouse, so it is up to the pups to rescue a rowboat drifting out to sea.

episodes.name: Pups Save Ryder
episodes.overview: When Ryder and a goat named Garbi are trapped on a ledge at Big View Trail, it is up to the pups to save them.

episodes.name: Pups Great Race
episodes.overview: It's Adventure Bay Race Day and the pups are about to race each other all across the town to see who is the fastest pup. One other competitor unexpectedly shows up though, Alex in his super trike!

episodes.name: Pups Take the Cake
episodes.overview: Mr.Porter enters a cake competition and needs Ryder and the pups to help him bake the biggest and tastiest cake. The race is on to get their cake baked and to the competition on time!

episodes.name: Pups and the Beanstalk
episodes.overview: Rubble has a wondrous dream, similar to Jack and the Beanstalk, where Marshall grows a giant beanstalk and Alex is a giant. However, when giant Alex starts to cause havoc, Ryder and the PAW Patrol must keep him occupied.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Turbots
episodes.overview: When Cap'n Turbot needs to get a picture of the rare Blue Footed Booby Bird when his French cousin, Francois Turbot, decides to help but gets caught on a cliff! It's up to the PAW Patrol to rescue him and bring the two cousins together again.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Camping Trip
episodes.overview: When Chickaletta falls in a cave in the ground it's up to the PAW Patrol to save her!

episodes.name: Pups and the Trouble with Turtles
episodes.overview: Tons of baby turtles are popping up all over the town. Can the PAW Patrol help get them back to their homes before they get hurt?

episodes.name: Pups Save the Space Alien
episodes.overview: An alien lands on Earth at Farmer Yumi's place, and the gang try to repair his spaceship so he can return home.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Flying Frog
episodes.overview: Marshall gets a pet frog, and it jumps into a helicopter prior to a big frog-jumping competition.

episodes.name: Pups and the Pirate Treasure
episodes.overview: Cap'n Turbot accidentally stumbles into a secret cavern that was once a pirate's hideout. When the PAW Patrol rescues him, they find an incomplete treasure map. The adventure is on as the pups follow clues to find the missing map pieces, and eventually to an amazing sunken pirate treasure!

episodes.name: Pups Save the Penguins
episodes.overview: The pups must find a way to get a group of penguins back to the South Pole.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Dolphin Pup
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol must help a Baby Dolphin get back into the bay with her parents.

episodes.name: Pups Save Jake
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol must rescue Jake when his ankle gets stuck between some fallen rocks.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Parade
episodes.overview: Katie's bathtub float floats away when Alex puts too many balloons on it during Adventure Bay Day.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Diving Bell
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol uses Zuma's new submarine to help Cap'n Turbot.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Beavers
episodes.overview: When a storm washes away Chompy the Beaver's dam, he starts chomping wood all over town.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Ghost
episodes.overview: A mysterious Ghost is causing havoc around the Lookout at night. The Pups and Chase in his new SPY GEAR set up a stakeout to bust it.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Show
episodes.overview: The Pups are going to put on a Medieval play in town square, but Cap'n Turbot's castle stage prop ends up collapsing and trapping him!

episodes.name: Pups Save an Ace
episodes.overview: Skye's favorite stunt pilot, Ace Sorensen, is heading to Adventure Bay to put on a fantastic air show. Just before arrival she runs into engine trouble!

episodes.name: Pups Save a Wedding
episodes.overview: Farmer Al and Farmer Yumi are getting married! Farmer Yumi's barn is being decorated for the big day and all the pups are helping, but a big storm blows in and takes down a wall of the barn!

episodes.name: The New Pup
episodes.overview: An Arctic storm picks up, but Jake finds help from a brave mountain ranger pup named Everest!

episodes.name: Pups Jungle Trouble
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol heads to the Jungle in the PAW Patroller to meet Ryder's 10 year old pen-pal, Carlos.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Herd
episodes.overview: Chase is taking part in a herding competition and starts to herd people around town as practice which causes more trouble than good.

episodes.name: Pups and the Big Freeze
episodes.overview: A wintertime storm causes trouble all over Adventure Bay.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Basketball Game
episodes.overview: Marshall is nervous about playing in the PAW Patrol basketball team. Chase lets Marshall sit out, but when Zuma and Rocky get injured, Marshall is forced to take over.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Talent Show
episodes.overview: It's Adventure Bay Talent Show Day! Mayor Goodway is excited but afraid there won't be enough acts! Ryder's super talented pups can definitely help out.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Corn Roast
episodes.overview: Ryder and the Pups help Farmer Al prepare his annual Corn Roast, complete with a Corn Field Maze! Bettina accidentally tips over some hot BBQ coals onto the piles of corn that begin to pop, pop, POP into piles of POPCORN!

episodes.name: Pups Leave Marshall Home Alone
episodes.overview: Ryder and the Pups head out for a day of Parachute training, but Marshall decides to stay back because of his fear of heights.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Deer
episodes.overview: Cap'n Turbot goes out ice fishing and finds a family of Deer stuck on the slippery ice! They must have tried to get across the frozen Bay for food! Ryder and the PAW Patrol to the rescue!

episodes.name: Pups Save a Friend
episodes.overview: Feeling like his clumsy ways are constantly messing up his friends' fun, Marshall decides to take a break from the PAW Patrol and goes off into the woods. Once the pups notice Marshall is gone, they jump to action to find him and bring him back to the Lookout.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Stowaway
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol is on another road trip--this time to the icy tundra to help Jake count penguins.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Parrot
episodes.overview: Ryder and the PAW Patrol head to the Jungle in the PAW PATROLLER to help their good friend CARLOS find his lost Parrot, Matea!

episodes.name: Pups Save the Queen Bee
episodes.overview: When Cap'n Turbot notices the light in his lighthouse isn't working properly, he discovers it's bee-cause a BIG beehive is inside it!

episodes.name: Pups' Adventures in Babysitting
episodes.overview: Mayor Goodway has her hands full with her twin niece and nephew Julia and Julius. She calls on the PAW Patrol to rescue them from a tree, and then twin sit for the day!

episodes.name: Pups Save the Fireworks
episodes.overview: Mayor Goodway receives a package of piglets instead of the fireworks she was expecting. It turns out that the mailman has been making sloppy deliveries as he keeps delivering each package to the wrong address.

episodes.name: Pups Save an Elephant Family
episodes.overview: The Pups are on a PAW Patroller road trip to the Savana where they meet up with Photo Safari fans Cap'n Turbot and his cousin François Turbot. In the middle of the night the campers are awakened by an intruder who turns out to be a lost baby elephant - Gilda.

episodes.name: Pups and the Mischievous Kittens
episodes.overview: Adventure Bay has been picked as a Finalist in the Tidiest Town Contest and looks like they're going to win! That is until Mayor Humdinger unleashes his Kitten Catastrophe Crew and those naughty kittens mess up everything in sight.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Mer-Pup
episodes.overview: When the Pups and Cap'n Turbot camp out under the very rare Magical Mer Moon, magical things begin to happen. Lured by the mystical Mer pup song and then transformed into Mer pups themselves, Skye and Zuma and even water resistant Rocky perform an underwater rescue in a sunken old ship. Cap'n Turbot and Ryder help out by diving deep to bottom of the Bay in their Diving Bell to help a Mer Mom and pup.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Sniffle
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol is just about to zoom off on their latest rescue to help Farmer Al capture his run-a-way pigs, Emma and Corny, when Chase sneezes, then Zuma sneezes and in a blink of an eye, Skye joins the group of sick puppies.

episodes.name: Pups and the Ghost Cabin
episodes.overview: It's spooky good times as Jake is cleaning up an old miner's cabin in the woods to revamp it as a ski chalet! Rubble and Rocky are happy to lend a helping hand, that is until their lunch disappears.

episodes.name: Pups Save an Adventure
episodes.overview: Alex is working towards getting his Action Scouts Fire Safety Badge, and who better to help him learn all about Fire Safety than Marshall and the PAW Patrol!

episodes.name: Pups Save a Surprise
episodes.overview: It's just another regular day in Adventure Bay as the PAW Patrol is called to duty. First they have to help Mr. Porter who has his rump stuck in a stump which turns out to be the home of a neighborhood skunk!

episodes.name: Pups Save the Mayor's Race
episodes.overview: It's the annual Mayor's Race and Mayor Goodway is determined to give it her best.

episodes.name: Pups Save an Outlaw's Loot
episodes.overview: Ryder helps Mayor Goodway sort through the old cabin of Outlaw Wild Wilbur when they come across a map for his buried treasure.

episodes.name: Pups Save Walinda
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol must come to the rescue when Wally's special friend, Walinda, gets tangled in an anchor chain.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Big Bone
episodes.overview: Cap'n Turbot and his cousin are in the middle of an archaeological dig when the cliff they are on collapses all around them.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Floundering Francois
episodes.overview: Cap'n Turbot and his cousin Francois are watching white whales in Adventure Bay when their boat hits a rock and starts to sink.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Pop-Up Penguins
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol must track down some loose penguins and help them return to the land of ice and snow.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Pizza
episodes.overview: While delivering special pizza dough for a party, Alex and Mr. Porter get into an accident.

episodes.name: Pups Save Skye
episodes.overview: A storm causes Skye to crash land in the snow while on her way to Jake's Mountain.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Woof and Roll Show
episodes.overview: When a storm blows through the town right before a concert, the pups must work together to clean up the mess.

episodes.name: Pups Save an Eagle
episodes.overview: Mayor Goodway's backpack slips down the side of a cliff with Chickaletta in it.

episodes.name: Pups Bark with Dinosaurs
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol is on a big excavation dig in the jungle with Cap'n Turbot looking for dinosaur fossils when they unearth 3 fossilized eggs. Before they know what's happening the eggs start to hatch and there are three baby pterodactyls running around Adventure Bay!

episodes.name: Pup-Fu!
episodes.overview: While Sensei Yumi teaches all the Pups the ancient art of Pup-Fu, Mayor Humdinger steals an ancient scroll that holds all the secrets of the art.

episodes.name: Pups Find a Genie
episodes.overview: Rubble Finds an old brass Jack-in-the-box with a Genie inside who grants him 3 wishes.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Tightrope Walker
episodes.overview: Francois tries to walk a tightrope from Adventure Bay's Bridge to the Lookout.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Snowboard Competition
episodes.overview: Jake and Everest are excited today's the day of the big Snowboard Competition, until they look outside and see the course is completely buried under blanket of snow.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Chicken of the Sea
episodes.overview: The Cap'n is about to test it out in an underwater adventure when Chickaletta, Cali and a seagull beat him to it. All the animal activity on the control panel drives the diving bell to the bottom of the bay.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Soccer Game
episodes.overview: The pups discover that their opponents in a soccer match are cheating.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Lucky Collar
episodes.overview: Marshall wins a supposedly lucky collar, leading him to take unnecessary risks while helping Cap'n Turbot save an owl.

episodes.name: Air Pups
episodes.overview: Cap'n Turbot and Francois go on a monkey communication expedition, but are put in danger when the volcano on the island erupts. The PAW Patrol uses their new Air Patroller to rescue the two, along with a family of monkeys.

episodes.name: The Pups Save Friendship Day
episodes.overview: While celebrating Friendship Day, the pups must prevent Mayor Humdinger from ruining Adventure Bay's reputation as the friendliest town on the map.

episodes.name: Pups Save Alex's Mini-Patrol
episodes.overview: The pups prepare for Adventure Bay's Tree Dedication Ceremony and end up receiving help from Alex Porter's newly-formed "mini-patrol."

episodes.name: Pups Save a Lost Tooth
episodes.overview: The pups' boat ride with Cap'n Turbot is postponed when they must track down a lost tooth.

episodes.name: Pups Save Daring Danny X
episodes.overview: Ryder uses the Air Patroller to save a wannabe daredevil.

episodes.name: Pups in a Fix
episodes.overview: Cap'n Turbot's boat, the Flounder, is tuned up by Ryder's robotic pup.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Dragon
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol performs a play in which Katie is a princess in a tower.

episodes.name: Pups Save Three Little Pigs
episodes.overview: Rubble builds a brick house for three pigs on a farm.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Goldrush
episodes.overview: The pups search for gold using Rocky's makeshift sifting tools.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Paw Patroller
episodes.overview: The pups take a break from washing the PAW Patroller. When they return, the PAW Patroller is missing.

episodes.name: Pups Save Apollo
episodes.overview: Rubble dreams about saving his idol, Apollo the Super-Pup, from an evil Spider King.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Hippos
episodes.overview: Zuma feels left out when he cannot assist in a mission involving a trio of circus hippos.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Polar Bears
episodes.overview: While on a trip to the Arctic, Cap'n Turbot needs the pups' help to get a family of polar bears back together.

episodes.name: A Pup in Sheep's Clothing
episodes.overview: Marshall puts on a sheep costume to find missing lambs on a farm.

episodes.name: Pups Save a School Bus
episodes.overview: Rocky uses his tools to repair the tires on a school bus.

episodes.name: Pups Save Old Trusty
episodes.overview: The pups discover that Adventure Bay's geyser, Old Trusty, has been plugged up by a boulder.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Pony
episodes.overview: The PAW Patroller gets stuck while the pups try to find a lost horse.

episodes.name: All Star Pups!
episodes.overview: The pups compete against a team of monkeys as part of a charity kickball game.

episodes.name: Pups Save Sports Day
episodes.overview: The pups build a halfpipe ramp so that Everest can compete in a sporting event.

episodes.name: Tracker Joins the Pups!
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol's newest member, Tracker, helps find an ancient crown.

episodes.name: Parroting Pups
episodes.overview: Rocky loses his voice while visiting Tracker in the jungle, so a talkative parrot helps him fulfill his PAW Patrol duties.

episodes.name: Merpups Save the Turbots
episodes.overview: Cap'n Turbot and Francois try to catch magical mer-pups on film. When they accidentally lure a giant sea slug on top of their diving bell in the process, the mer-pups must rescue them.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Robo-Saurus
episodes.overview: The pups set out to recover a missing robotic dinosaur.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Film Festival
episodes.overview: The pups have trouble filming their entry for a film festival.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Stinky Flower
episodes.overview: Rocky turns his recycling truck into a boat so that he can bring a foul-smelling plant across the bay.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Monkey-naut
episodes.overview: A monkey's space mission turns into a rescue after Cap'n Turbot finds out that the spaceship's hatch is broken.

episodes.name: Pups Bear-ly Save Danny
episodes.overview: The boy from "Pups Save Daring Danny X" returns and tries to outperform Everest at snowboarding.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Mayor's Tulips
episodes.overview: Chase and Rocky are left in charge of guarding Mayor Goodway's tulips.

episodes.name: Pups Get Growing
episodes.overview: The pups must stop overgrown tomatoes from rolling around Adventure Bay.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Space Toy
episodes.overview: Marshall is beamed into the sky by space aliens.

episodes.name: Pups in a Jam
episodes.overview: The pups take care of an ant infestation on the day of Adventure Bay's jam festival.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Windsurfing Pig
episodes.overview: Zuma tracks down a pig on a windsurfing board.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Gliding Turbots
episodes.overview: Cap'n Turbot and Francois break their hang glider while doing research on albino monkeys.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Plane
episodes.overview: A flock of seagulls damages a wing flap on a plane that the mayor is piloting.

episodes.name: Pups Get Skunked
episodes.overview: The pups' hunt for berries is cut short when Everest is sprayed by a skunk.

episodes.name: Pups and a Whale of a Tale
episodes.overview: During a whale watching trip, Cap'n Turbot finds a baby whale trapped under an ice sheet.

episodes.name: The Pups' Winter Wonder Show
episodes.overview: Tracker helps out when the pups need to find Cap'n Turbot's skating penguins, who have gone missing during a blizzard.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Giant Plant
episodes.overview: Tracker's new Venus flytrap grows at an unexpected rate after being planted in an unsuitable area.

episodes.name: Pups Get Stuck
episodes.overview: Rubble's electromagnet falls into Marshall's fire truck, magnetizing the vehicle and causing problems around the town.

episodes.name: Pups Raise the PAW Patroller
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol must find a way to save their waterlogged 18-wheeler after it sinks to the bottom of Adventure Bay.

episodes.name: Pups Save the Crows
episodes.overview: Two crows start to steal objects from around Adventure Bay, including hats needed for the town's "Hat-a-palooza" event.

episodes.name: Pups Save Their Floating Friends
episodes.overview: A "floating ray" from outer space causes the people of Adventure Bay to float in mid-air.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Satellite
episodes.overview: The PAW Patrol must stop an out-of-orbit satellite from crashing in time to catch Rubble's favourite TV show.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: The PAW Patrol pups take their adventures to the sky with an all-new rescue vehicle, the Air Patroller, that can transport Ryder and the gang anywhere in the world. The third season also introduces new friends including Tracker, a jeep-driving pup with super hearing who lives in the jungle with Carlos.

episodes.name: Pups Save a Blimp
episodes.overview: Capn' Turbot's weather blimp is taken by Mayor Humdinger, who plans to use it to change the weather in Foggy Bottom.
